    "        \"Difference in group means\",\n",
    "        \"Slope beta1\",\n",
    "        \"Slope beta1\",\n",
    "        \"Difference in rank distributions\",\n",
    "        \"Slope beta1 on ranks\",\n",
    "        \"Whether paired differences center around zero\",\n",
    "        \"Intercept beta0 on signed ranks\"\n",
